column5: Hi Everyone, Headed to this area on Friday, July 15 and wondering if anyone has any recent fishing reports? We fish mostly in an area north of Taylor Island and northeast of Maclean's Narrows to Bear Narrows. Thanks for any info you are willing to share. Big Louie
I'll be curious to hear how you do, I'm headed up the week after you. Good luck
Big Louie, I will be fishing that location the last week in July. If you would, please pm me on this site or email fishing info to [email protected] Thanks and good luck!
Headed up there first week of August and fishing out of lost island lodge let me know how you guys do.
